/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281727594/image_1281727594.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281727594/image_1281727594.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281727594/image_1281727594.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Alex Potemkin</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p><strong>Martinrea International Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MRETF\" title=\"Martinrea International Inc.\">OTCPK:MRETF</a>)</strong>, a Tier One, small-cap company out of Canada, makes car parts for automakers worldwide. They focus on lightweight, high-tech components, supplying metal parts, assemblies, and aluminum pieces to big names in the car business with operations in 55 locations across ten countries, including</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281727594/image_1281727594.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743423-martinrea-international-undervalued-with-strategic-growth-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 01:25:43"}, {"id": "4743420", "title": "uniQure's AMT-130: A Bold Step For Huntington's, But Not Without Hurdles", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Blue glowing neuron with axons template\" data-id=\"1277345854\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sakkmesterke</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>uniQure N.V.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QURE\" title=\"uniQure N.V.\">QURE</a></span>) is a Netherlands-based company that develops and manufactures gene therapies for rare diseases. AMT-130 is a gene therapy aimed at slowing the progression of Huntington's disease [HD]. <a href=\"https://www.uniqure.com/programs-pipeline/huntingtons-disease\" rel=\"nofollow\">AMT-130</a> \u201cconsists of an AAV5</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1277345854/image_1277345854.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743420-uniqure-amt-130-bold-step-for-huntingtons-but-not-without-hurdles", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 01:20:46"}, {"id": "4743419", "title": "Super Micro Computer: Deep Dive Into The Special Committee's Conclusions", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://s