(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRDF\" title=\"Cardiff Oncology, Inc.\">CRDF</a></span>) has just <a href=\"https://investors.cardiffoncology.com/news-releases/news-release-details/cardiff-oncology-announces-positive-initial-data-first-line-ras\" rel=\"nofollow\">announced</a> initial data from its Phase 2 trial in metastatic colorectal cancer, confirming dose-related outperformance of standard of care. At the same time, Cardiff has <a href=\"https://investors.cardiffoncology.com/news-releases/news-release-details/cardiff-oncology-prices-oversubscribed-40-million-underwritten\" rel=\"nofollow\">announced</a> a $2.6 pricing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269082820/image_1269082820.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743418-cardiff-beats-standard-of-care-in-first-line-metastatic-colorectal-cancer", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 01:05:28"}, {"id": "4743377", "title": "Protara Therapeutics: Carving New Roads In Bladder Cancer", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Standing out from the Crowd concept 2\" data-id=\"1808744976\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/